                     <interp inst="t18311020-169-person1167" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Lamb's-court, Bunhill-row. I went with Beresford to search for the prisoner; I found this bundle - I do not know whether the prisoner used the left; I have seen him wear these trousers.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-169-person1168">
